ield will take place in the unusual slot of late July. Both the Emirates Stadium and the London Stadium showed their interest in keeping the game in London but their efforts have been rebuffed.   By Emmanuel Okogba The Community Shield tie between Manchester City and Liverpool which is the curtain raiser for a new season has been moved from Wembley to Leicester City's King Power Stadium. This development follows the final of the Women's Euro 2022 coming up the following day at the Wembley… In "Sports" Nigerian music superstar, Fireboy DML on Wednesday night broke down in tears after performing his hit song "Peru" with Ed Sheeran at the Wembley Stadium, London. The Wembley Stadium has about 90,000 capacity, and will have Ed Sheeran perform for five nights from 24 June to 1 July. Recall that… In "Entertainment" By Emmanuel Okogba Liverpool and Jurgen Klopp are accessing the fitness of Mohamed Salah Virgil Van Dijk to ascertain their chances of featuring in Tuesday's must-win Premier League tie away to Southampton. Salah and Van Dijk were both substituted earlier than usual in their FA Cup victory over Chelsea last… In "Sports"